				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Your talking past each other again.
<br />

<br />
You both know that adding 80 DPS at the top end to our pets is probably about right to balance us.  It would put us back into the endgame, and if it scaled back to 50 or 55, it would do a LOT to even us out in our problem areas.
<br />

<br />
You also both know that the likelihood that this will happen is marginal at best for two big reasones.  First, EQ devs have been terrified of the mage, because mages are hard to balance.  Especially with the whole limited pallete of powers vision we are dealing with now.  Second is perceptions, we have even MORE perception of effortlessness when everything goes right than even the quadders have, (though not looking as uber as bard swarm kites).  What people don't see is the balancing act, when we are pushing it.  Also, we farm greens like no-ones business, and classes like the kiters and the rotters do not have nearly the steepness in difficulty curve as we do, so when they see us plow through greens that they still have to work at, they assume that we scale just like them, so that we are JUST as efficient versus XP mobs.
<br />

<br />
Anyway, lets not keep going back and forth on this, when you  aren't even fighting the same fight.<br />_________________<br />Rondo</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
